# This repo is developed on macOS and also edited by a Claude Code instance
# running on the Parallels Windows VM, against the SAME working tree on the
# shared volume. Without normalisation, Windows' autocrlf would rewrite every
# line ending and make a one-line edit look like a whole-file change.
#
# Normalise everything to LF in the repo AND in the working tree on both sides.
# .NET, PowerShell 5.1 and git all read LF-only files without complaint.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binaries git must never touch.
*.png  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.af   binary
*.icon binary
